<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="References">References</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Perpetual_foreigner&amp;action=edit&amp;section=10" title="Edit section: References"><span>edit</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
<div class="reflist">
<div class="mw-references-wrap mw-references-columns"><ol class="references">
<li id="cite_note-1"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-1">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><cite id="CITEREFLoh-Hagan2022" class="citation book cs1">Loh-Hagan, Virginia (January 1, 2022). <i>What is the Forever Foreigner Stereotype?</i>. 21st Century Skills Library. Cherry Lake Publishing. <a href="/wiki/ISBN_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="ISBN (identifier)">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/9781668900505" title="Special:BookSources/9781668900505"><bdi>9781668900505</bdi></a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=What+is+the+Forever+Foreigner+Stereotype%3F&amp;rft.series=21st+Century+Skills+Library&amp;rft.pub=Cherry+Lake+Publishing&amp;rft.date=2022-01-01&amp;rft.isbn=9781668900505&amp;rft.aulast=Loh-Hagan&amp;rft.aufirst=Virginia&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3APerpetual+foreigner" class="Z3988"></span></span>
